  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\nIn  >50% cases custom mailserver is disconnected after relogin.\r\nIt is blocker for part of 5767 e2e.\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/108862793-dd47c080-75f0-11eb-8145-86bf21ba9a68.png)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nConnected to custom mailserver\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nConnected to another mailserver\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to Sync settings > status nodes\r\n- Disable autoselection\r\n- Add custom status node and connect to it\r\n- Relogin and check if still connected to custom status node\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: .nightly 23/02/21\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nVideo: https://app.saucelabs.com/tests/c07b8f5e27bc47a685a00999b91f5794?auth=b848bb8076c8299657844be0dc725e70#127\r\n[logcat (1).log](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/6029717/logcat.1.log)\r\nExample of failed e2e: https://ethstatus.testrail.net/index.php?/tests/view/2173353\r\n",
